- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also likely as the paper deals with tree automata and language non-emptiness tests. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses a new approach to constructing and pruning a state space. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper discusses the implementation of a decision procedure. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses a method for efficiently solving a logical problem.
